          <msContents>
            <summary>Manuscript was used for contemplation and study and is a short Hindu philosophical treatise written from the perspective of the Advaita (non-dualism) Vedanta school of philosophy. The work deals especially with issues of the traditional caste system and purity.</summary>
            <textLang>In Sanskrit</textLang>
            <msItem>
